 spin of the central MBH with unprecedented precision and we can determine\nhow the holes \"eat\" stars that happen to be near them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 May 2012 18:04:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 09:28:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2018 20:39:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
